config BR2_PACKAGE_CITRUSPILOT
	bool "citruspilot"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_HAS_UDEV
	select BR2_PACKAGE_FFMPEG_V4L2REQUEST
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBDRM
	help
	  Low-latency FPV video player for the Orange Pi Zero 2W (Allwinner
	  H618): take the drone's H.265 off the wfb-ng link (de-FEC'd RTP on a
	  local UDP port), hardware-decode on Cedrus, and scan direct-to-plane
	  on the DE33 display engine. The sunxi analog of PixelPilot_rk.

	  Player only -- it consumes the RTP that an external wfb_rx forwards
	  to udp:5600. Requires the v4l2request-patched ffmpeg
	  (ffmpeg-v4l2request) and the patched mainline kernel (NV12 on the
	  DE33 VI plane).

	  https://github.com/gilankpam/citruspilot
